Clan Law
Long ago, on the lost continent of Kunark, an Ancient order was established, The Jade Dragon Clan.  With the discovery of Kunark by out the "Outsiders" came change.  All maner of new beings ventured forth into the land.  Instead of shuning the change like most of the Iksar on Kunark had, The Jade  embraced it.  They took upon thier ranks all manner of beings.   Elves, Humans, Orgres, Trolls, Gnomes and many others... This of course made the Clan hated by other clans of this lost realm... But also feared as there numbers still continue to grow...
